    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A building type found in gardens, built in secluded, quiet areas and used for studies or studios. Such buildings are generally enclosed and located deep within the garden.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
